    <item>
      <title>原油价格波动至七个月低点附近，因股市下跌抵消了伊朗风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中东地区紧张局势加剧，金融市场普遍出现抛售，交易员担心伊朗可能对以色列采取报复性打击，油价在七个月低点附近波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-5</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 23:10:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其通胀料将大幅下降，央行或将忽视</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/turkish-inflation-set-for-huge-drop-that-central-bank-may-ignore</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其7月份整体通胀率可能出现近两年来最大幅度下降，这一放缓主要是由于基数效应，而官员们可能由于关注更直接的价格风险而忽视了这一效应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/turkish-inflation-set-for-huge-drop-that-central-bank-may-ignore</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
